    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Been fighting with DNS over VPN really killing my local chef testing from home. After some digging around you need to set this in the kitchen.yml (or kitchen.local.yml):</p>

<p>``` yaml kitchen.yml
driver_config:</p>

<h1>&hellip;</h1>

<p>  customize:</p>

<pre><code>natdnshostresolver1: "on"
</code></pre>

<p>```</p>

<p>Hopefully this will save someone a headache.</p>
]]></content>
